{"tid":654622,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個同初戀既第一次","createTime":"2018-05-05T19:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T21:02:04.000Z","uid":182163,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4051fa0a49ac8d00ef2818c17effae38fcabd3","tid":654622,"uid":182163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:33:53.000Z","msg":"係第一次出街！出街！<br />\n好想知啲人第一次拍拖 第一次出街係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夜晚訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139de46f016d8e34d959513955d2c219efd56692","tid":654622,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:35:54.000Z","msg":"食飯行街"},{"pid":"0167f408f5b423ead71cb130fcbf2fcc734c845a","tid":654622,"uid":144513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:38:07.000Z","msg":"尷尬到唔敢講嘢 對望 手都唔敢拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e9a5c6ff0b1f2c5469a87a5d3d5ee3636c0edb","tid":654622,"uid":71579,"like":12,"dislike":49,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:43:16.000Z","msg":"淨係記得第一次錫<br />\n坐喺佢張床度望住<br />\n佢無啦啦就一嘢錫埋嚟<br />\n嗰種觸電嘅感覺<br />\n第一次感受到女人温唇嘅質感<br />\n之後就係咁打茄輪<br />\n嗰陣覺得感覺好似啜緊三文魚 好滑<br />\n一錫就錫咗一個鐘 扯到硬曬<br />\n但係因為好愛佢 唔想好似沾污咗佢咁 冇出到<br />\n過幾日佢就生日了<br />\n我係唔會再同佢講生日快樂㗎<br />\n但如果你睇到依度應該知道我講緊你<br />\n我唔會唔記得<br />\n但係已經唔重要啦<br />\n希望你以後開開心心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f47fa9078fe2285864108fbe8c8375169a73a8","tid":654622,"uid":163558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:50:36.000Z","msg":"第一次拖手 係落小巴之後<br />\n佢見我行得好慢就一野拖住我叫我行快啲<br />\n嗚啊成個身僵左啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ffab3618aa39c11b42c8c0f39bb46b163471a9","tid":654622,"uid":111625,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:57:30.000Z","msg":"同自己第一個鐘意既女仔係公司扑野<br />\n自為佢係我既初戀,原來我只係佢其中一個水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbff972b31ef8ff73b51078cfad80c51d0048d9d","tid":654622,"uid":15800,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"29f47fa9078fe2285864108fbe8c8375169a73a8","tid":654622,"uid":163558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:50:36.000Z","msg":"第一次拖手 係落小巴之後<br />\n佢見我行得好慢就一野拖住我叫我行快啲<br />\n嗚啊成個身僵左啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T21:06:33.000Z","msg":"好懷念呢個感覺，仲會好似有股熱流湧上大腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家就算同異性攬埋一舊都冇乜感覺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cc8336faf0ea59bea8ee177832189265a5d6ba","tid":654622,"uid":138522,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:39:16.000Z","msg":"冇初戀呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9873130892b6b7cb0237ffc7a104d3c23883b6d5","tid":654622,"uid":132587,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:42:28.000Z","msg":"第一次分手<br />\n由當初好熱情 到後尾好冷淡 <br />\n到最後佢好似變左第二個人咁<br />\n然後好快同左第二個一齊<br />\n完全瓦解左我對愛情睇法"},{"pid":"eaa561ec0b8d7735a8e23136713555a9a3e7ede3","tid":654622,"uid":185434,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:48:45.000Z","msg":"第一次拖手，第一次kiss，第一次抱，第一次信哂對方，第一次比對方見自己的缺點，第一次啪啪啪，第一次因爲對方喊左幾個鐘，第一次比男仔哄，第一次收花"},{"pid":"b156274c5eb5e97d9fba73e3150fd307c6cb7400","tid":654622,"uid":116705,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:50:27.000Z","msg":"第一次係度屌鳩樓主！那有女呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383d16de04e0bcfe5d63c2af43b12ed4623c2039","tid":654622,"uid":172693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"一齊訓會肉緊到訓唔到"},{"pid":"4ba6e0c5afbfbc327c5e0b0b0ffe93cf82003ca2","tid